  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/339658f8e4cf85243d2f81a5afaa55e9.poster.avif?t=1695752998\" width=588 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/339658f8e4cf85243d2f81a5afaa55e9.webm?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/339658f8e4cf85243d2f81a5afaa55e9.mp4?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Warning: This game may potentially trigger epileptic seizures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First-person horror game with random events.</h2><br>You play as a janitor (called “Hausmeister” in German) who takes care of an apartment building.<br>The people living in the building will call you on the phone or ring your doorbell, to tell you about an issue they expirience.<br>You will then recieve a note, that tells you what to do.<br>Sometimes you have to grab the cleaning tools from the supply room, and use them.<br>Some other time, you will have to have a talk with one of the residents.<br>Among other things, you fix broken pipes, change light bulbs, mop the floor, and mow the lawn. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/6a72a7f00187173446750e997274ace3.poster.avif?t=1695752998\" width=730 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/6a72a7f00187173446750e997274ace3.webm?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/6a72a7f00187173446750e997274ace3.mp4?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Everything changes, when you realize that you are being haunted by an angry spirit.<br>Get ready to be spooked by random ghost encounters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/62a9861dd4f3c8c59b29e02a0cbaed41.poster.avif?t=1695752998\" width=730 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/62a9861dd4f3c8c59b29e02a0cbaed41.webm?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/62a9861dd4f3c8c59b29e02a0cbaed41.mp4?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You have to uncover the mystery about the old woman who lives on the top floor of the building. <br>Who is she? What is she?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/339658f8e4cf85243d2f81a5afaa55e9.poster.avif?t=1695752998\" width=588 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/339658f8e4cf85243d2f81a5afaa55e9.webm?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/339658f8e4cf85243d2f81a5afaa55e9.mp4?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Warning: This game may potentially trigger epileptic seizures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First-person horror game with random events.</h2><br>You play as a janitor (called “Hausmeister” in German) who takes care of an apartment building.<br>The people living in the building will call you on the phone or ring your doorbell, to tell you about an issue they expirience.<br>You will then recieve a note, that tells you what to do.<br>Sometimes you have to grab the cleaning tools from the supply room, and use them.<br>Some other time, you will have to have a talk with one of the residents.<br>Among other things, you fix broken pipes, change light bulbs, mop the floor, and mow the lawn. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/6a72a7f00187173446750e997274ace3.poster.avif?t=1695752998\" width=730 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/6a72a7f00187173446750e997274ace3.webm?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/6a72a7f00187173446750e997274ace3.mp4?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Everything changes, when you realize that you are being haunted by an angry spirit.<br>Get ready to be spooked by random ghost encounters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/62a9861dd4f3c8c59b29e02a0cbaed41.poster.avif?t=1695752998\" width=730 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/62a9861dd4f3c8c59b29e02a0cbaed41.webm?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064580/extras/62a9861dd4f3c8c59b29e02a0cbaed41.mp4?t=1695752998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You have to uncover the mystery about the old woman who lives on the top floor of the building. <br>Who is she? What is she?",
